  <brief_title>Phase 2 Study of Velusetrag in Diabetic or Idiopathic Gastroparesis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo- Controlled, Phase 2 Study to Evaluate Velusetrag Effects on Gastric Emptying in Subjects With Diabetic or Idiopathic Gastroparesis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
